OL,3,C'My daughter was a crime scene': Holly
OL,4,CNewton's mother recalls daughter's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FThe mother of murdered Hexham teenager
OL,8,FHolly Newton has said she was unable
OL,9,Fto touch her in hospital because "my
OL,10,Fdaughter was a crime scene".
OL,12,FMicala Trussler read out a powerful
OL,13,Fstatement in Newcastle Crown Court for
OL,14,Fthe first day of the sentencing of her
OL,15,Fdaughter's killer - 17-year-old Logan
OL,16,FMacPhail.
OL,18,FHolly was just 15-years-old when she
OL,19,Fwas stabbed to death in Hexham in
OL,20,FNorthumberland in January 2023 by
OL,21,FMacPhail, who was her ex-boyfriend.
