OL,3,C'My daughter was a crime scene': Holly
OL,4,CNewton's mother recalls daughter's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FMacPhail was 16 at the time of the
OL,8,Fmurder and could not be named during
OL,9,Fthe trial because of his age. However,
OL,10,Fa judge at Newcastle Crown Court
OL,11,Flifted a reporting restriction earlier
OL,12,Fthis month, so that the media could
OL,13,Fname him.
OL,15,FDuring the trial, the court heard
OL,16,FMacPhail had stalked Holly around the
OL,17,Ftown centre of Hexham before stabbing
OL,18,Fher and causing 36 injuries to her
OL,19,Fbody.
