OL,3,C'My daughter was a crime scene': Holly
OL,4,CNewton's mother recalls daughter's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FMs Trussler told the court today that
OL,8,Fshe raced to the scene of the attack
OL,9,Fand was frightened of what she would
OL,10,Ffind in Hexham city centre that day.
OL,12,F"The enormity and severity cannot be
OL,13,Fput into words," she sad. "I was
OL,14,Fstopped from seeing my daughter in the
OL,15,Falleyway and the ambulance due to the
OL,16,Fhorrifying condition she was in."
OL,18,FThe statement continued: "My daughter
OL,19,Fdied not knowing her mam was by her
OL,20,Fside.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/9
