OL,3,C'My daughter was a crime scene': Holly
OL,4,CNewton's mother recalls daughter's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FHer mother described MacPhail as mild-
OL,8,Fmannered and polite during his regular
OL,9,Fvisits to their home in Haltwhistle,
OL,10,FNorthumberland.
OL,12,FBut things changed when Holly matured
OL,13,Fand decided to end the relationship,
OL,14,Fher mother said.
OL,16,FShe believed her daughter was the
OL,17,Fvictim of domestic abuse and was
OL,18,Fcaused emotional turmoil by her ex-
OL,19,Fboyfriend.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G5/9
