OL,3,C'My daughter was a crime scene': Holly
OL,4,CNewton's mother recalls daughter's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FHe changed her social media passwords
OL,8,Fand made Holly believe he could hack
OL,9,Finto her accounts, as well as
OL,10,Fthreatening to self-harm.
OL,12,FMacPhail travelled to her home the
OL,13,Fnight before the murder and hung
OL,14,Faround for hours, trying to convince
OL,15,Fone of her siblings to let him in.
OL,17,F"I dread to think what could have
OL,18,Fhappened to the rest of my family had
OL,19,Fhe been allowed inside," Ms Trussler
OL,20,Fsaid.
