OL,3,C'My daughter was a crime scene': Holly
OL,4,CNewton's mother recalls daughter's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FDavid Brooke KC, prosecuting, pointed
OL,8,Fout the teenager was able to get to
OL,9,FHaltwhistle from his home in Birtley
OL,10,Fin Gateshead alone the night before
OL,11,Fthe murder, to follow Holly around
OL,12,FHexham while disguised and lie to her
OL,13,Fabout his whereabouts.
OL,15,F"He was perfectly able to make
OL,16,Frational choices," Mr Brooke said.
OL,18,FMacPhail was convicted of murder, as
OL,19,Fwell as wounding with intent on a boy
OL,20,Fwho stepped in to try to stop the
OL,21,Fattack.
