OL,3,C'My daughter was a crime scene': Holly
OL,4,CNewton's mother recalls daughter's
OL,5,Cmurder
OL,7,FMacPhail, who met Holly when they both
OL,8,Fattended Army cadets, claimed he never
OL,9,Fplanned to attack her but wanted to
OL,10,Fuse the knife to kill himself.
OL,12,FMacPhail denied murder but admitted
OL,13,Fmanslaughter, claiming he blacked out,
OL,14,Fbut his story was rejected by the jury.
OL,16,FThe sentencing continues.
